Dialogue: 1,0:00:04.65,0:00:08.57,Narration,Takasu Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,There's something in this world that nobody has seen yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:21.70,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H805320&\fs27\frz24.129\fnEssai\pos(447.272727,117)}Fluffy bangs give a gentle expression
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:21.70,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnEssai\3c&H805320&\fs27\frz32.522\pos(643.636364,453)}Gently capture women's hearts
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.08,0:00:21.70,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,This reeks...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.37,0:00:25.79,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,of being fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:31.96,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz33.408\pos(710.909091,171)\c&H000000&\3c&HF2D6DF&}Mold
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.76,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell. It's getting moldy again.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.76,0:00:34.93,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,And I recently wiped off the mold too.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.05,Narration,Ryuuji (loud),0000,0000,0000,,It's something gentle and very sweet.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.51,0:00:38.55,Default,Ryuuji (mumbling),0000,0000,0000,,Where did I put that rag...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.97,0:00:44.39,Narration,Ryuuji (loud),0000,0000,0000,,And if you had been able to put your eyes on it, then you would yearn for it.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.44,0:00:52.28,Narration,Aisaka Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the world has hidden it.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.28,0:00:55.07,Narration,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,To make sure that not just anyone can get their hands on it.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.91,0:00:58.68,Default,Ryuuji (mumbling),0000,0000,0000,,Shit, I can't wipe it off!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.03,0:01:03.12,Narration,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,But at some point, someone will find it.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.29,0:01:08.67,Narration,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That one person who is supposed to find it is also the one who will be able to find it.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.55,0:01:17.26,Narration,Taiga & Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's just how it is.{orig: It's simply set up that way.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:25.69,Ep Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(1016.363636,307.5)}Tiger & Dragon
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.56,0:01:25.94,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eco, eco, eco, ecology~
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.77,0:01:35.13,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Inko-chan, you're still resting? It's morning already.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.65,0:01:38.74,Default,Takasu Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,I got you!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.70,0:01:47.42,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,How cold of you, Ryuu-chan.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.42,0:01:49.92,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I told you last night that I have school from today on, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.92,0:01:54.59,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the opening ceremony.\NCongratulations on passing last year.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.59,0:01:57.76,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Should you really be sarcastic towards your son when he's going into his new school year?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.76,0:02:01.76,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the room is dark. Open the curtains!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.76,0:02:02.72,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,They're open.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:10.94,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\bord1.5\frz331.259\3c&HC9F5EE&\c&H242C28&\move(963.636364,318,963.636364,780)}The Takasu House
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.64,0:02:09.27,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,That's a huge apartment building.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.27,0:02:11.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of people live there.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.61,0:02:16.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,After it was built, the sun quit shining here and our laundry doesn't dry well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:13.90,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H262C28&\3c&HCFF4F1&\frz342.688\move(905.454545,0,905.454545,192)}HERE
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.99,0:02:19.36,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Every morning there's mold, moldiness, heaps of mold...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.36,0:02:23.70,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,That sharp look! You're beginning to look more and more like your dad!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.70,0:02:27.08,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,3380)}...more and more like your dad! {echo}
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.08,0:02:28.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't compare me to tha—!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.54,0:02:33.04,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so cool! Even more like your dad!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.46,0:02:40.72,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you leaving already? What about my meal?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.09,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's where it always is.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.22,0:02:44.18,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.18,0:02:50.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That was the only thing I didn't want to hear.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.94,0:03:00.36,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of this look in my eyes, which you always praise, that I... I...{It's because of this look in my eyes, which mom always praises, that I look like a deliquent and people are scared shitless of me.}
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.57,Default,Random guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.24,0:03:06.95,Default,Random guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takasu!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.95,0:03:08.58,Default,Random guy,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.96,Alternative,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What? Wh—
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.58,0:03:09.58,Default,Random guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.29,Default,Random guys,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept this and spare us!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.96,Default,Random guys,0000,0000,0000,,This is all we have! It's true!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.67,Default,Random guys,0000,0000,0000,,S-See? We're not annoying you, are we?!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.09,Alternative,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.01,Default,Random guys,0000,0000,0000,,WE'RE SORRY!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.26,0:03:22.34,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.41,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H252E2F&\3c&HAFCBDB&\fnAubrey\pos(640,0)\fs37.5}Lost and Found Items
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.41,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H252E2F&\bord0\3c&HAFCBDB&\fnAubrey\fs27\frx332\fry2\pos(689.090909,208.5)}Oohashi High School
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.41,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H252E2F&\bord0\3c&HAFCBDB&\fnAubrey\fs30\frx332\fry2\frz1.288\pos(627.272727,276)}General Affairs Department
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.68,0:03:32.60,Default,Man in window,0000,0000,0000,,Again? You sure pick up a lot of wallets.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.60,0:03:33.35,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.35,0:03:35.15,Default,Girls running by,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we end up in the same class again!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.15,0:03:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.32,Default,Girl #1,0000,0000,0000,,It's there!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.32,0:03:42.11,Default,Girl #2,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray, we're in the same class again!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.41,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, not this again...
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.41,0:03:51.25,Default,Kitamura Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.83,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same class again aren't we, Takasu?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.59,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:59.57,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\frz346.087\c&H000000&\3c&HEBE1E3&\bord2.25\move(303.636364,502.5,303.636364,453)\fnAnnifont\i1}Oohashi High School Opening Ceremony
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.00,0:04:00.88,Default,Speaker,0000,0000,0000,,And now this year's opening ceremony has ended.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.88,0:04:04.22,Default,Speaker,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please head towards your individual classrooms and prepare for homeroom.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.68,0:04:09.89,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,A new class. It seems that I have to start off by clearing up all the misunderstandings again.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.89,0:04:11.10,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.02,0:04:15.56,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,I already know, so it won't be necessary for everyone.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.73,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.73,0:04:23.24,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. There are people like him who understand.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.49,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,And in this class...
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.53,Default,Kushieda Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.33,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same class this year too!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.33,0:04:32.96,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,You're in class C too, Kushieda?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.84,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, right? Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.84,0:04:40.88,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I appear from time to time around Kitamura.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.26,0:04:45.01,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kushieda Minori, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.01,0:04:49.93,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you remembered my full name! I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.27,0:04:58.86,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,And with that, let us passionately enjoy class in high spirits!{original: eloquently enjoy class cheerfully}
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.86,0:04:59.44,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.44,0:05:00.86,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.94,0:05:03.44,Default,Punk,0000,0000,0000,,And then—
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.20,0:05:06.36,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Takasu?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.36,0:05:09.20,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I-I just need to go the bathroom.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.93,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll go on ahead.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.27,0:05:18.04,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.04,0:05:20.34,Default,Muttering in the background,0000,0000,0000,,Holy shit! He's already heading into a decisive battle!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.34,0:05:26.01,Default,More muttering,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu Ryuuji and Aisaka Taiga. The most dangerous ones are already clashing! {extending -F}
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.76,0:05:35.56,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, she's so small, just like a doll. But somehow...
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.44,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow there's this hateful...
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.44,0:05:43.23,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,As if you'd get eaten if you missed one step...
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.23,0:05:46.86,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it's true! The delinquent Takasu and the Palmtop Tiger are—!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.86,0:05:47.32,Default,Other girl,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.78,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HDBFDFC&\c&H4E5357&\fs30\frz25.011\pos(203.636364,108)\fnBeatsville}Ferocity of a tiger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:50.78,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnBeatsville\fs30\3c&HFAFAFA&\c&H464646&\pos(1080,297)\frz336.164}But small
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.95,0:05:50.78,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Palmtop... Tiger...?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.91,0:05:54.08,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! Palmtop Ti—
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.58,0:05:58.79,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Fits perfectly.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.80,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's it for today.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.80,0:06:08.93,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Those who haven't turned in the new questionnaire, please come to the faculty office later, okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.93,0:06:11.01,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.01,0:06:12.30,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.77,0:06:19.48,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Taiga? You were late.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.48,0:06:23.98,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the doctor, and he said that it's caused by house dust.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.98,0:06:27.28,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,A modern-day illness, must be tough.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.95,0:06:33.41,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,So the Palmtop Tiger is friends with Kushieda Minori.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.16,0:06:36.37,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The one with problems here is me.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.37,0:06:37.45,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.00,0:06:40.17,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.54,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.54,0:06:44.55,Default,Girl in background,0000,0000,0000,,They were amazing, Aisaka-san and Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.63,Default,Guy in background,0000,0000,0000,,The Palmtop Tiger sure is strong.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.63,0:06:49.55,Default,Guy #2 in background,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, Takasu only {\i1}looks{\i0} scary. He's not actually a delinquent.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.55,0:06:50.47,Default,Girl #2 in background,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.47,0:06:52.43,Default,Yuusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Seems it will be easier to clean up the misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.39,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, 'sup?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.31,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.44,0:07:05.02,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takasu-kun, you aren't lost about where to go with your life are you...?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.02,0:07:05.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.61,0:07:08.90,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bu-Bu-But... I really need you to turn in your questionnaire.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.90,0:07:11.07,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,All of the other students have submitted theirs already.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.16,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry, I forg—
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.62,0:07:14.58,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I'M SO SORRY! I'M SO SORRY!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.33,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want some stranger coming in and telling you what to do
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.33,0:07:17.83,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,while you're still deciding on what to do with your life, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.12,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:21.48,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frx0\fry16\frz357.255\pos(569.090909,592.5)\bord0\shad2.25\bord0.75\3a&H96&\4c&H92A6C6&\c&HAED8E8&\be1}Fire Cabinet
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.37,0:07:23.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.29,0:07:25.79,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Time Zero will be ove-
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.15,Default,Ryuyuji,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay...?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,My bag, my bag...
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.16,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just leave her be...
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.70,0:07:56.49,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-!
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.08,0:08:00.29,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What ar- What are you do- What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.16,0:08:00.12,Alternative,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What are you—
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.37,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I just came here to get my—
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.37,0:08:06.46,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's your bag?! Isn't your seat the ne-
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.34,0:08:12.09,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I got the placements of the seats mix- mixed—!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.77,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she want my bag?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.69,0:08:24.48,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it already!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.03,0:08:33.20,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,WHY, YOU!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.07,0:08:36.78,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aisaka?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.41,0:08:43.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.21,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,IDIOT!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.76,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,She's a mess.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.45,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,This room too.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.23,0:09:12.44,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad is in heaven, you see.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.94,0:09:19.20,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,He was so cool! He'd hide weekly magazines behind his shirt in case he got stabbed.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.78,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going numb just from the thought!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.78,0:09:23.08,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Just because I look like you...
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.37,0:09:26.29,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having mountains of trouble you know!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.00,0:09:31.92,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't have this face, no one would be afraid of me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.92,0:09:34.47,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,and I wouldn't end up getting involved with the Palmtop Tiger.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.26,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have more faith in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.51,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H4C4643&\bord2.25\3c&HE3E1DF&\fnComplete in Him\fs37.5\frz359.921\pos(594.545455,534)}Best Driving Collection - Spring
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.72,0:09:39.51,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.72,0:09:43.33,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, the new questionnaire.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.02,0:09:47.23,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
