Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:50.73,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H675962&\fnBudHand\b1\fs30\pos(656.363636,283.5)\frx356\fry332\frz15.214}From Aisaka Taiga
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:50.88,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H675962&\fnBudHand\b1\fs30\frx354\fry344\frz10.97\pos(698.181818,277.5)}From Aisaka Taiga
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:52.42,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H675962&\fnBudHand\b1\fs30\frz9.799\pos(741.818182,276)}From Aisaka Taiga
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.52,0:09:54.36,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,From... Aisaka Taiga?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.36,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.87,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,"You put this in my bag by mistake, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.87,0:10:06.62,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine what's inside since I didn't peek!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.62,0:10:08.58,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll just return it to you then!"
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.67,0:10:12.46,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, I got to reseal it!
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.34,0:10:21.30,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,She... She's one hell of a klutz, isn't she?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.68,0:10:25.68,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Gunna sleep.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.66,0:10:44.24,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko isn't supposed to be home yet... right?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.24,0:10:47.16,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, let's drink more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:49.02,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz9.974\3c&H5C31C4&\fnVAG Rounded Std Light\pos(867.272727,303)}Takasu Yasuko\N{\fs24\b1}Professional Name: Mirano
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:49.02,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVAG Rounded Std Light\pos(918.181818,489)\frz351.3\c&H80332B&\3c&HF5F5F7&}At work
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Heeey...
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.47,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The window's...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.57,0:11:17.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I know someone this small...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,AISAKA!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.75,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,USE A TISSUE!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.09,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.76,0:11:49.18,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What the...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.18,0:11:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...hell..
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.18,0:11:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.10,0:11:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...doing?!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.56,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about it.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.11,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about...?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.94,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that le—
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.86,0:12:01.57,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,-tter....
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.11,0:12:07.45,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer live on now that you've found out about that. I have to die!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.31,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't try to kill me!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.31,0:12:12.08,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die, so I've got to kill you!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.66,0:12:15.92,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Or... you could forget all about it!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.92,0:12:17.25,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.96,0:12:25.39,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay, I'll just hit you on the head with this. Even if I can't kill you, I can send your memories flying away.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.55,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't send them flying!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.55,0:12:28.64,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, that lette-
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.64,0:12:29.26,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.02,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.35,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,SHUT UP, SHUT UP!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.35,0:12:34.31,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it, didn't you?! You read it, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.31,0:12:36.48,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to tell you, I didn't-
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.48,0:12:37.81,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No, that won't do.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.81,0:12:44.55,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,So you have to forget all about that l-l-love letter!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.86,0:12:46.78,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,IT WAS EMPTY!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.70,0:12:53.41,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Em...pty...?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.87,0:12:57.08,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There was nothing inside.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.46,0:13:00.57,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky you didn't turn it over to Kitamura.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.57,0:13:02.97,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,So let's just leave this failure be and—
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.05,0:13:06.22,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.31,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Just how hungry are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.90,0:13:23.32,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I got tired of the convenience store.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.32,0:13:26.38,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Convenience store? What, don't your parents fe—
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.99,0:13:30.24,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has their family issues, I guess.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.03,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.66,0:13:40.73,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If you had just had quietly handed over the bag earlier, things wouldn't have ended up like this.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.17,0:13:43.26,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,How do you intend to make up for it?!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.63,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's still stuck to your face.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.01,0:13:52.35,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing that from a guy who was born only to add the scent of garlic to the oil used in this fried rice...
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.81,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen here...
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.52,0:14:05.32,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,How is a love letter embarrassing?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.32,0:14:09.28,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You see, that's not even close to being embarrassing. Just wait.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.58,0:14:13.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Behold!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.25,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.67,0:14:22.04,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what that is? You don't, do you?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.04,0:14:27.92,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's a list of songs I would use if I were to put on a concert for the girl I like.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.51,0:14:31.26,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's a poem I created for her without realizing it.{"without thinking", "by accident", "naturally"}
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.39,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Minidiscs to play while I'm on a car trip with her.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.39,0:14:34.72,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a license, of course.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.72,0:14:36.85,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I have plans laid out for all seasons of the year.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.44,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Disgusting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.44,0:14:43.02,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Since I don't have the guts to confess to her, I just have to imagine like this.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.57,0:14:47.40,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's horribly miserable, but I don't think of it as embarrassing!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.03,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to have faith in yourself!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.65,0:14:53.74,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You've gone beyond imagining and went and took action!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.74,0:14:57.16,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to think about the future, passionately, in high spirits!
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.29,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,"I present to this to thee, Kushieda Minori."
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.29,0:15:02.33,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, just like Kushieda Minori!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.33,0:15:03.50,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.38,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,So you like Minori?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.38,0:15:07.13,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,How impudent.{lol geass flashbacks}
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.84,0:15:09.42,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Learn your place.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.84,0:15:12.47,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You're not the one to talk!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.47,0:15:14.72,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?! You said you'd forget!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.47,0:15:20.44,Default,Inko-chan,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Goose, goosebumps!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.89,0:15:23.48,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Inko-chan. Did we wake you?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.48,0:15:26.02,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What are you showing me? How disgusting!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.02,0:15:28.57,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying about my precious family?!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.24,Default,Inko-chan,0000,0000,0000,,I— I—
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.24,0:15:33.45,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Are you going to present yourself to the visitor, Inko-chan?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.45,0:15:35.62,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and say your name!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.62,0:15:38.75,Default,Inko-chan,0000,0000,0000,,In{\alpha&HFF&}po!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.75,0:15:39.33,Default,Inko-chan,0000,0000,0000,,Inpo!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.75,0:15:48.26,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, you see, Inko-chan isn't feeling well today...
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.26,0:15:51.17,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it's already this late!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.63,0:15:57.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,E-Either way, we're birds of the same feather! I won't tell anyone about the letter! Can't you be okay with that?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.60,0:15:58.22,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.22,0:16:01.73,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! No wait, you've already gotten a meal, just leave!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.73,0:16:05.73,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, please leave? My wacky mom is about to come home!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.31,0:16:07.02,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,NO {\alpha&HFF&}FUCKING WAY!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.02,0:16:07.57,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,NO FUCKING {\alpha&HFF&}WAY!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.57,0:16:08.32,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,NO FUCKING WAY!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.90,0:16:11.03,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust you.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.49,0:16:13.28,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And besides...
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.82,0:16:19.24,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,How are love letters? They're not fashionable anymore, are they?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.24,0:16:21.91,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you fidgeting now?!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.91,0:16:27.04,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you advice on romantic relationships any time, but it's already late, so how about tomorrow...?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.46,0:16:31.13,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You'll help me?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.13,0:16:33.59,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I will. I will I will I will! I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.05,0:16:40.56,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Anything, right? You'll obey me like a dog? You'll do anything to the extreme?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.93,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I will. I swear!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.31,0:16:46.35,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,So, let us just end it at that, okay? Okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.65,0:16:54.91,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,How did she get in through the window?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.20,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.82,0:16:57.62,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk you home.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.62,0:17:00.54,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay. It's close, and I got this wooden sword.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.54,0:17:01.83,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's just dangerous.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.04,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That hole...
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.79,0:17:10.32,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that? I can just cover it up with some paper.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.38,0:17:11.96,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.80,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You can use this.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.63,0:17:18.43,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If it ends up costing money, I'll pay you later.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.01,0:17:21.26,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.26,0:17:22.72,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.39,0:17:28.19,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, did she just call me by my first name?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.41,0:17:47.25,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is the Takasu residenc—
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.25,0:17:48.63,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,GET THE HELL OVER HERE! YOU'RE—
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.22,0:17:56.63,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.63,0:17:57.55,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You hung up, didn't you?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.76,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Come over where?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.81,0:18:03.52,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.64,0:18:08.90,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The veranda, why?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.31,0:18:12.48,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,HOW?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.48,0:18:15.74,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd do anything, just like a dog, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.74,0:18:19.53,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that was about yesterday's thing about Kitamura—
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.53,0:18:23.95,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't come, you know what will happen, don't you? I can show you what will happen if you want me to...
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.95,0:18:26.12,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you see...
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.75,0:18:31.42,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait ten more minutes! The seasoned rice will be done in ten more minutes!
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.13,0:18:33.21,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Three?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.97,0:18:42.35,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You want some too?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.07,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.33,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.04,0:19:11.75,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's open?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.01,0:19:19.17,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this smell?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.26,0:19:23.35,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka-san, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.18,0:19:26.39,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Something smells horrible.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.06,0:19:35.23,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,AISAKA! {NEATFREAK RAGE!}
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.07,0:19:41.20,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka. Aisaka! AISAKA!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.20,0:19:42.24,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Your kitchen!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.39,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to—!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.91,0:19:46.95,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Please, allow me to clean your kitchen!
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.96,0:19:55.59,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What, sleeping again?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.13,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,She looks handcrafted...
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.80,0:20:06.14,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The sleeping Aisaka really looked like a doll.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.85,0:20:11.56,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The house had no trace of anyone really living there. It looked like it was part of someone's doll house.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.69,0:20:16.82,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,But it was too large to be someone's doll house.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.78,0:20:23.11,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take fifteen minutes, I guess.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.49,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.01,0:20:46.05,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What's... this...?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.85,0:20:51.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.68,0:20:55.65,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still at it, but it's a lot cleaner now isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.35,0:20:57.69,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It was horrid!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.69,0:20:59.65,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The water clogged up in the sink was rotten.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.65,0:21:03.26,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The drainage was awfully moldy and all the waste was like hell spawn.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.61,0:21:05.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,And the room was full of dust-
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.28,0:21:11.83,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Trespassing. Forced cleaning. You didn't go around marking the place, did you, dog?!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.83,0:21:12.95,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,DOG?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.95,0:21:17.58,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to apologize to the other dogs. You're a mongrel of a dog.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.58,0:21:18.79,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Mon-grel.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.79,0:21:22.67,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What an ungrateful bitch, when other people have...!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.56,0:21:33.48,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's your table prayer?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.27,0:21:39.90,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Dear god of rice and producers of this product, I thank you for this meal!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.11,0:21:42.38,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh you...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.61,0:21:46.65,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, your nose stopped dripping.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.20,0:21:50.12,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, since the room's all clean...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.16,0:21:52.24,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.08,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,SHUT UP!
