Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.58,0:21:56.92,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0015,,Disoriented agreement.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.92,0:21:57.67,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0015,,Surfacing misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.67,0:21:59.13,Default,Ryuiji,0000,0000,0015,,The power of genes.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.13,0:22:00.75,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0015,,Taiga, you...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.75,0:22:02.63,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0015,,You're one hell of a klutz.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.63,0:22:04.38,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0015,,Shut up and rot.
